data.description: This historic 2 story home is situated on a large corner lot.  The covered wrap around front porch will invite you inside where you are welcomed by the gorgeous woodwork and hardwood floors!  This home has been completely re-done down to the studs in 2014, everything including electrical and plumbing has been updated!  The large original windows throughout the home allow for great natural lighting.  The living room has a huge all wood pocket door to allow for separation from the dining room.  The kitchen has been completely updated including white cabinets, quartz countertops and SS appliances.  1st floor laundry and small office space with a full bath finish off the 1st floor. Upstairs has 3 bedrooms and a 3/4 bathroom. Located right across the street from Colfax-Mingo Elementary.  Colfax is a charming little town 25 min east of Des Moines.  All information obtained from Seller and public records.
